{"article_id":"8ZUA4Iu72rdTjzzC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Tuesday called for a `` good shutdown '' in September","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to fix the `` mess \" in government .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"He also expressed frustration","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that legislation needs 60 votes in the Senate","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"because of the filibuster ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"it would be necessary to elect more Republicans","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"or `` change the rules . ''","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"`` The reason for the plan","depth":13},{"id":9,"text":"negotiated between the Republicans and Democrats","depth":13},{"id":10,"text":"is that we need 60 votes in the Senate","depth":13},{"id":11,"text":"which are not there !","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"We either elect more Republican Senators in 2018","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"or change the rules now to 51 % .","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"Our country needs a good 'shutdown ' in September","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"to fix mess ! ''","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"he wrote in a series of tweets .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"The reason for the plan","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"negotiated between the Republicans and Democrats","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"is that we need 60 votes in the Senate","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"which are not there !","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"We ....","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"May 2 , 2017","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"either elect more Republican Senators in 2018","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"or change the rules now to 51 % .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Our country needs a good `` shutdown '' in September","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"to fix mess !","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"May 2 , 2017","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Trump 's unprecedented comments appear to reflect frustration with the spending deal","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Congress is poised to approve this week .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"The legislation would fund the government through September","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and represents the first major bipartisan legislation of Trump 's presidency .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Democrats have argued","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"that they won most of the battles","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"surrounding the bill ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"and several media accounts have suggested","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"that Trump and the White House were losers in the negotiations .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"A New York Times headline on the deal said :","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"`` Winners and Losers of the Spending Deal","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"( Spoiler Alert :","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Trump Lost ) . ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"White House budget director Mick Mulvaney expressed frustration with that analysis during a press briefing after Trump 's remarks .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Trump himself said ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"`` this bill is a clear win for the American people '' during a ceremony","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"honoring the Air Force Academy football team .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"The measure will spare the president a damaging government shutdown ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"but it left out many of his biggest policy requests .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"It does not include funding for Trump ' s proposed wall along the U.S.-Mexico border","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"or include language","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"stripping federal money from so-called sanctuary cities ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"both of which the White House demanded at the outset of negotiations .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"The White House also backed off a threat","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"to withhold ObamaCare subsidy payments to insurance companies .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Trump was forced to abandon those demands","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"after Democrats in the Senate threatened to block the spending bill","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"if they were included .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The president did secure increased military spending in the 2017 budget deal ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"breaking with longstanding practice","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that a boost in Pentagon spending be accompanied by dollar-for-dollar spike in domestic spending .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Ryan trumpeted that provision as a \" game-changer. \"","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Mulvaney also defended the president 's threat of a shutdown in the fall .","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"\" The president ' s tweet was that we might need a shutdown at some point","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"to drive home that this place -","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that Washington needs to be fixed , \"","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"\" I think","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"that 's a defensible position , one","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"we 'll deal with in September . \"","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Mulvaney argued","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"the current deal","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"running through September","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"was a White House victory","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"because Democrats were determined to cause a shutdown","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"that would hurt Trump .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"\" They wanted a shutdown .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"They wanted to try and make this president look like he could not govern , ''","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"`` They wanted to make this president look like he did not know what he was doing .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"And he beat them on that at the very , very highest level .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"`` They were desperate to show","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"that we were not reasonable","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"and we completely destroyed that narrative","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"by negotiating this deal , ''","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Trump ' s comments are likely to irk top Republican lawmakers ,","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"who have been frustrated by Trump ' s repeated attempts","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"to intervene in the legislative process .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Cornyn did not mention the president or his tweets ,","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"but his remarks about the importance","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"of avoiding a shutdown","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"and the strength of the filibuster were notable","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"coming shortly after Trump 's tweets .","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"`` We were elected to govern .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Yes , governing is hard .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"It 's hard by design . ...","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"But that 's the way","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"our founding fathers designed our constitutional system , ''","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"he said .","depth":4},{"id":102,"text":"If GOP lawmakers are frustrated with Trump , however ,","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"the feeling may be mutual .","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"The businessman-turned-president has vented frustration with the slow pace of work on Capitol Hill .","depth":4},{"id":105,"text":"\" I ' m disappointed","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"that it doesn ' t go quicker , \"","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"Trump told Fox News last week","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"when asked about the Republican effort","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"to repeal and replace ObamaCare .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":200,"right":218,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":200,"left":173,"right":199,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":141,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"